{"tid":540870,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"X-Men: Dark Phoenix搵Hans Zimmer 配樂","createTime":"2018-01-26T01:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T02:39:45.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3308fe05b59ac50e6402e41284f8ec18a1fffa2","tid":540870,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T01:39:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/hans-zimmer-return-superhero-movies-scoring-x-men-dark-phoenix-1078456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fheat-vision%2Fhans-zimmer-return-superhero-movies-scoring-x-men-dark-phoenix-1078456&d=ya9at78alSX84WIc7iBEagCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=090ce228\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/hans-zimmer-return-superhero-movies-scoring-x-men-dark-phoenix-1078456</a><br />\n<br />\nZimmer announced in March 2016 that he wouldn&rsquo;t be working on any more superhero movies after Batman v. Superman: Dawn of Justice, saying that after so long inside the genre, he&rsquo;d had his fill. &ldquo;I did Batman Begins with Chris [Nolan] 12 years ago, so The Dark Knight Trilogy might be three movies to you, to me it was 11 years of my life,&quot; he said, adding that BvS &ldquo;was very hard for me to do, to try to find new language.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nApparently, the chance to relax did wonders. Dark Phoenix star Evan Peters revealed the news on MTV's Happy Sad Confused podcast, immediately adding, &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know if I was supposed to say that or not.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"62309527796aab90799847449e3eb588ca5a2af2","tid":540870,"uid":64796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T01:43:55.000Z","msg":"又話唔再配英雄片？"},{"pid":"6fe2a695865ac4c80802eab165111e511e337358","tid":540870,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"62309527796aab90799847449e3eb588ca5a2af2","tid":540870,"uid":64796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy